_sText:
The file is saved as "building"

This is an apartment building that I designed roughly after one in a picture I saw. 

I grouped the entire building, so it is easier to move



Only the building is in the VMF, none of the scenery.



It is hollow inside and has no roof.

If there's enough interest I could take time and make an inside :)



Also the screenshots are really crappy :/

Please make sure you credit me any time this prefab is used! :)
